{"tid":1484200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死我，交通popo沿路封路俾示威者，引人去西環，點知冇人上當","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:36:28.000Z","uid":30743,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7f49f095a0faf2b512a56ba3c89a771c5cecaa","tid":1484200,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"朋友發夢sd 過黎<br />\n<br />\n由中環停車場開始有班交通popo , 見隊頭行到佢地個位，就set雪糕筒封路走人， 去下一個街口<br />\n<br />\n之後就set到交易所出面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkP3cjy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkP3cjy.jpg&h=fbd73ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知set完都冇人行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEk9SkX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEk9SkX.jpg&h=b26b3b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直set到去上環，都係冇人行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuhL97R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuhL97R.jpg&h=bb3cf304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個位都封，有個司機心諗做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落車移開雪糕駛走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mzbmeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mzbmeV.jpg&h=d0d6bd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中環一帶無人佔路，但係又塞車，都係popo搞出黎"},{"pid":"e95331fcc967f7be9c0d20f4599b2b07af2caa6e","tid":1484200,"uid":30743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"封撚晒都冇人理呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef6ce55d29df374c2ce9e84087cb6f1f6db23d5","tid":1484200,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,